<paragraph blockId="37.[151,1436,220,894]" box="[151,1175,220,242]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,163,220,241]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">1</emphasis>
(a) Head with lateral sutures divergent forward and not connected with antennal furrows (
<figureCitation box="[1075,1133,220,242]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="37.[151,250,1614,1638]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,918,1586]" captionTargetId="figure-342@37.[151,1436,918,1590]" captionTargetPageId="37" captionText="FIGURE 1. Key to tribes and genera 1" figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6876495" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6876495/files/figure.png" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">Fig. 1</figureCitation>
: 1a)
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="37.[151,1436,220,894]" box="[199,659,249,271]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">
(b) Forewing with vein Sc1 absent (
<figureCitation box="[558,616,249,271]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="37.[151,250,1614,1638]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,918,1586]" captionTargetId="figure-342@37.[151,1436,918,1590]" captionTargetPageId="37" captionText="FIGURE 1. Key to tribes and genera 1" figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6876495" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6876495/files/figure.png" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">Fig. 1</figureCitation>
: 1b)
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="37.[151,1436,220,894]" box="[199,1293,279,301]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">
(c) Lancet with lamnium enlarged (
<figureCitation box="[554,612,279,301]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="37.[151,250,1614,1638]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,918,1586]" captionTargetId="figure-342@37.[151,1436,918,1590]" captionTargetPageId="37" captionText="FIGURE 1. Key to tribes and genera 1" figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6876495" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6876495/files/figure.png" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">Fig. 1</figureCitation>
: 1c). 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Benson" authorityYear="1945" box="[666,793,279,301]" class="Insecta" family="Pamphiliidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="37" pageNumber="97" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="tribe" tribe="Neurotomini">Neurotomini</taxonomicName>
